Vitreoretinal Consultants of NY is the premier retinal care destination for patients across Long Island, Queens, NYC, and beyond. Founded in 1981, our team of nationally-recognized retina specialists and surgeons have established themselves as distinguished physicians, compassionate providers, and key thought leaders in the retina care community. Vitreoretinal Consultants of NY are committed to providing a compassionate and ethical environment that focuses on patient-centered care. From diagnostics to clinical trials, Vitreoretinal Consultants of NY bring clarity, transparency, and humanity to all aspects of what we do.
